    Package Description

    Model classes of the Aggregator.
    energy.usef.agr.model.device.capability
    Model classes of aggregator device capabilities.

    Repository classes of the Aggregator.
    energy.usef.agr.service.business

    energy.usef.agr.transformer

    This package contains aggregator utility functions.
